contents.desc: Depth. The extent, measurement, or distance downwards, backwards, or inwards.

No one understands the depths it takes to operate in this situation quite like the community rescue team who have by hand, and body lowered and lifted thousands of kilograms of people, living and deceased; food and supplies.¬†¬†

We are grateful that collective actions have mobilised to get the state to start a rescue operation. Please continue to support the Backabuddy for Emergency Relief to Trapped Miners to provide direct aid to the Stilfontein miners, families and community.¬†
